1. The strategy for each one of the automated players:
- Clever player go over the board line by line from left to right and from top to bottom and choose the first empty
cell.
- Genius player go over the board column by column, starting from the second column, from top to bottom and choose the
first empty cell.

2. The advantage of the program pattern design by which all the players implement a common interface is that ...
- Program to interface and not to implementation

